TITLE: Defining Message Structure in Protobuf
DESCRIPTION: Specifies the structure of a Message in the Farcaster network, including fields for data, hash, signature, and related schemes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/farcasterxyz/snapchain/blob/main/site/docs/pages/reference/datatypes/messages.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: protobuf
CODE:
```
message Message {
  MessageData data = 1;
  bytes hash = 2;
  HashScheme hash_scheme = 3;
  bytes signature = 4;
  SignatureScheme signature_scheme = 5;
  bytes signer = 6;
  bytes data_bytes = 7;
}
```

